snippet.title: ARCH WIZARD early teaser
snippet.description:
ARCH WIZARD is a fast paced "Hyper Shooter" complemented with esoteric exploration experience. Take a quest to become Arch Wizard: dominate surrounding realms, reverse Time, escape Death, befriend Chaos, face the End of the World.
Knowledge based progression. High scores. Full of secrets.

Development in process:
toster12d3.bsky.social

Music: Komiku - 11 Action Epic
